			<div class="panel-body ">
				<p>One of the many ways to earn Cash is by completing <a href="{$config.url}quests">missions</a> successfully.</p>
				<p>One other productive task would be <a href="{$config.url}job">taking on a job</a> as often as possible.</p>
				Most enjoyable is attacking hackers directly through <a href="{$config.url}grid">the Grid</a> or by taking part in Organization and Zone wars.
