			</div>
			<div class="panel-body text-right">
				<p><strong>You need to <a href="{$config.url}shop">buy (CHEAP) server components and software</a> to <a href="{$config.url}servers/build/do">build your first MAIN server</a>.</strong></p>
				<p><a href="{$config.url}quests">Missions</a> are means for you to gain experience, skills, money, achievements and notoriety.</p>
				
				
				
				
				<p>
					Mission groups become available as you fulfil their requirements. Selected few missions are available only <a href="{$config.url}parties">in party</a> and some can be redone daily rewarding you each time while others can be repeated unlimitedly with no rewards.
					</p>
				You will be exposed to an <a href="http://bit.ly/1jcUBP6" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><strong>UNIX-ish terminal</strong></a>, learning commands that you can even use outside of this world.
			</div>
			<div class="panel-footer">
